@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v2
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.exp(tmp + 0.11) / 0.23))
    tmp = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.86) / v1) - wp.sin((v2 + 0.46 + v2 + 0.99)))
    v1 = ((wp.exp(v0 + 0.64) - (v2 + 0.77 - v2 + 0.97)) - ((v0 + 0.71 * tmp + 0.11) * tmp))
    v1 = v1
    tmp = v1
    tmp = tmp
    v2 = 0.60
    data[tid] = v0
